       IDENTIFICATION   DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.      prog.
       DATA             DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE  SECTION.
       01 ONE   PIC 9 VALUE 1.
       01 TWO   PIC 9 VALUE 2.
       01 THREE PIC 9 VALUE 3.
       PROCEDURE        DIVISION.
           IF THREE = ONE AND TWO OR THREE
               DISPLAY "OK"
